133
00:08:51,088 --> 00:08:52,722
"Senzai ichiguu"
(A fated meeting that occurs once in a thousand years.)

134
00:08:52,722 --> 00:08:54,706
Yea,
that will definitely come out in the next exam.

135
00:08:54,706 --> 00:08:56,882
"Senzai ichiguu"?

136
00:08:58,081 --> 00:08:59,029
I've got it!

137
00:08:59,029 --> 00:09:02,333
It means, when doing the washing,
one should use one full cup of detergent.
("Sentaku" is the washing of clothes,
"Senzai" is detergent,
"Ichi" is one)

138
00:09:02,323 --> 00:09:03,868
That's it, right?

139
00:09:03,868 --> 00:09:04,928
Right...

140
00:09:04,928 --> 00:09:07,409
Senzai... Ichi... Guu... - One cup of washing detergent
("Senzai" is detegent,
"Ichi" is one)

141
00:09:07,409 --> 00:09:08,557
Wrong!

142
00:09:08,557 --> 00:09:12,005
Then what's the right answer?

143
00:09:11,105 --> 00:09:15,926
An opportunity that comes once
in a thousand years.

144
00:09:16,201 --> 00:09:17,119
Oh that's it.

145
00:09:17,119 --> 00:09:17,907
For example...

146
00:09:17,907 --> 00:09:20,810
There's someone you really like
but he already has a girlfriend.

147
00:09:20,810 --> 00:09:25,039
But then suddenly, he decides to break up with her,
and becomes available again.

148
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:28,969
That would be a "Senzai Ichiguu" chance.
So it's used like that.

149
00:09:28,969 --> 00:09:30,972
So that's how it is.

150
00:09:30,972 --> 00:09:32,491
I'm full already.

151
00:09:32,491 --> 00:09:34,884
Tsukushi, why don't you eat another bowl?

152
00:09:34,884 --> 00:09:36,497
Well...

153
00:09:37,265 --> 00:09:41,008
My stomach is already very full.

154
00:09:41,008 --> 00:09:42,635
Then, I'm done eating as well.

155
00:09:42,635 --> 00:09:44,373
The dishes are still hot, why leave now?

156
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:47,004
I still feel bloated.

157
00:09:46,804 --> 00:09:48,977
My stomach feels like it is inside out.

158
00:09:48,977 --> 00:09:51,341
Well said, kid.

159
00:09:51,441 --> 00:09:55,201
You made a joke, just like me.
Your level has just gone up.

160
00:09:56,171 --> 00:09:58,027
We shouldn't joke about love relationships.

161
00:09:58,127 --> 00:09:58,951
What?

162
00:09:58,951 --> 00:10:00,563
She's been acting weird

163
00:10:00,563 --> 00:10:03,645
ever since she came back from the party.

164
00:10:03,645 --> 00:10:08,782
Maybe... She's already in a relationship
with one of those rich guys.

165
00:10:09,779 --> 00:10:13,631
So it's our family status,
that causing her to be uneasy about it.

166
00:10:13,631 --> 00:10:15,041
Is that for real?

167
00:10:15,041 --> 00:10:17,523
That girl is really serious about
dating one of those rich guys?

168
00:10:17,523 --> 00:10:21,137
Well isn't that a "Senzai ichiguu" chance?
(A fated meeting that occurs once in a thousand years.)

169
00:10:21,864 --> 00:10:23,946
We're going to be rich!!

170
00:10:26,116 --> 00:10:30,109
"Senzai ichiguu"...

171
00:11:15,935 --> 00:11:19,767
Sanjou Sakurako doesn't even dare to come to school

172
00:11:19,767 --> 00:11:23,046
You really aren't afraid of anything.

173
00:11:23,046 --> 00:11:25,636
Yeaa...

174
00:11:25,636 --> 00:11:26,832
Huh?

175
00:11:26,832 --> 00:11:30,133
It's rumoured that she has left the school.

176
00:11:30,133 --> 00:11:31,048
Eh?

177
00:11:34,454 --> 00:11:36,984
It really is your fault that she became like this.

178
00:11:36,984 --> 00:11:40,786
And you still dare to come to school
as if nothing happened.

179
00:11:46,959 --> 00:11:50,287
They're right about me not wanting to go to school.

180
00:11:52,246 --> 00:11:55,425
I'm sorry.
It's all my fault.

181
00:11:56,747 --> 00:11:58,068
No.

182
00:12:01,019 --> 00:12:02,778
Tsukushi-chan,

183
00:12:03,824 --> 00:12:08,663
I heard that you kissed Doumyoji at the party.
Is that true?

184
00:12:08,663 --> 00:12:11,542
What kiss?
It was an accident.

185
00:12:15,421 --> 00:12:16,523
Don't worry.

186
00:12:16,523 --> 00:12:18,731
He won't bother you again.

187
00:12:23,309 --> 00:12:25,420
Sakurako-san

188
00:12:26,269 --> 00:12:29,965
I'll always be by your side.

189
00:12:32,743 --> 00:12:36,180
You can always look me up
if you feel lonely or troubled.

190
00:12:45,838 --> 00:12:47,557
See you.

191
00:13:00,637 --> 00:13:03,570
Oh goodness.
If I don't hurry...

192
00:13:08,394 --> 00:13:09,865
This is horrible.

193
00:13:09,865 --> 00:13:11,126
Oh!

194
00:13:11,126 --> 00:13:12,961
It's you.

195
00:13:12,961 --> 00:13:14,078
What a coincidence.

196
00:13:14,078 --> 00:13:17,521
If you stop the car there,
it will block the pedestrians.

197
00:13:18,695 --> 00:13:20,772
I heard that you've been skipping classes.

198
00:13:20,772 --> 00:13:22,375
It's none of your business.

199
00:13:22,375 --> 00:13:23,193
Huh?

200
00:13:23,193 --> 00:13:24,740
Aren't you skipping classes as well?

201
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:26,276
I'm going for my classes now.

202
00:13:26,276 --> 00:13:28,470
Oh? Well then...
I'm going back.

203
00:13:28,470 --> 00:13:30,483
Hey hey...

204
00:13:30,483 --> 00:13:31,924
The last time you kissed me

205
00:13:31,924 --> 00:13:34,095
be sure not to fall in love with me.

206
00:13:34,095 --> 00:13:35,531
Huh??

207
00:13:35,531 --> 00:13:37,666
Have you lost your mind?
I really don't get you.

208
00:13:37,666 --> 00:13:38,434
Get in.

209
00:13:38,434 --> 00:13:39,564
What?

210
00:13:39,564 --> 00:13:42,174
I'll give you a lift to school, so get in.

211
00:13:42,174 --> 00:13:44,967
W... Wait...
Let me go!

212
00:13:44,967 --> 00:13:46,769
This is unbelievable!

213
00:13:46,769 --> 00:13:48,237
What are you saying, you...

214
00:13:50,653 --> 00:13:52,194
Stop there!!

215
00:14:03,825 --> 00:14:05,002
That girl runs really fast...

216
00:14:06,543 --> 00:14:08,285
Don't be such an idiot!

217
00:14:13,883 --> 00:14:15,153
It can't be...

218
00:14:29,327 --> 00:14:30,700
What?

219
00:14:35,813 --> 00:14:37,396
Wh... What?

220
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:40,906
It hurts, sis!

221
00:14:43,174 --> 00:14:44,690
Sister?

222
00:14:52,841 --> 00:14:54,073
Hi there.

223
00:15:04,145 --> 00:15:06,908
Why is Makino Tsukushi with Ms Tsubaki?

224
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:09,229
You can always contact me at this address.

225
00:15:09,229 --> 00:15:10,408
Yes

226
00:15:11,747 --> 00:15:14,529
Los Angeles??

227
00:15:14,529 --> 00:15:18,276
If Tsukushi-san calls me,
I'll fly back immediately.

228
00:15:18,276 --> 00:15:19,885
Fly back...

229
00:15:19,885 --> 00:15:21,739
In a private jet.

230
00:15:22,618 --> 00:15:23,852
You're serious about flying back.

231
00:15:23,852 --> 00:15:25,230
I'm stopping over in Japan for a while.

232
00:15:25,230 --> 00:15:27,066
If I have time, I'll have a meal with you.

233
00:15:27,801 --> 00:15:28,827
Umm...

234
00:15:28,827 --> 00:15:32,687
Why are you so nice to me?

235
00:15:33,128 --> 00:15:36,259
That idiot of a brother seems to be giving you some trouble.

236
00:15:36,259 --> 00:15:38,638
Then again,

237
00:15:38,638 --> 00:15:41,363
Two people can really have similar tastes.

238
00:15:41,363 --> 00:15:42,219
Huh?

239
00:15:42,219 --> 00:15:43,733
You and I...

240
00:15:47,919 --> 00:15:48,956
My my...

241
00:15:48,956 --> 00:15:51,381
You're as innocent as Tsukasa.

242
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:55,962
Perhaps he really likes you, Tsukushi-chan.

243
00:15:55,962 --> 00:15:56,851
Hmm?

244
00:15:56,851 --> 00:15:58,775
Well then, see you. Look me up anytime.

245
00:15:58,775 --> 00:15:59,551
Oh...

246
00:15:59,551 --> 00:16:00,571
Okay.

247
00:16:01,951 --> 00:16:03,800
Thank you very much.

248
00:16:08,358 --> 00:16:10,515
So cool...

249
00:16:11,065 --> 00:16:12,787
Ah! So cool!!!

250
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:42,526
Madam.
(Literally, Madam Representative)

251
00:16:42,526 --> 00:16:45,581
Ms Tsubaki has returned today.

252
00:16:45,581 --> 00:16:46,898
Tsubaki?

253
00:16:46,898 --> 00:16:48,808
Yes, that would be the older sister.

254
00:16:48,808 --> 00:16:52,618
If she has any private matters,

255
00:16:53,164 --> 00:16:54,283
Nishida,

256
00:16:54,283 --> 00:16:55,578
prepare his retirement grant and lump sum pay.

257
00:16:55,578 --> 00:16:56,362
Yes ma'am.

258
00:16:56,362 --> 00:16:57,474
Do it by today.

259
00:16:57,474 --> 00:16:58,282
Madam!

260
00:16:58,282 --> 00:16:59,482
Please wait a minute!!

261
00:16:59,482 --> 00:17:00,997
Please wait!

262
00:17:00,997 --> 00:17:02,226
Let me go!

263
00:17:05,134 --> 00:17:06,563
The meeting will now begin,

264
00:17:06,563 --> 00:17:10,292
for the temporary board of directors
of the Doumyoji Group.

265
00:17:10,292 --> 00:17:11,152
Madam.

266
00:17:11,152 --> 00:17:13,346
This concerns the remaining issues we have

267
00:17:13,346 --> 00:17:15,976
