290
00:18:27,069 --> 00:18:28,400
Maybe you just want to live with your sis again?

291
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,998
Don't say such disgusting things.

292
00:18:32,568 --> 00:18:34,516
Well,

293
00:18:34,516 --> 00:18:35,576
