294
00:18:35,576 --> 00:18:37,595
About a week.

295
00:18:41,157 --> 00:18:44,993
Don't look so lonely, I'll be back real soon.

296
00:18:44,993 --> 00:18:47,408
It doesn't really matter if you're back or not.

297
00:18:47,965 --> 00:18:50,275
Well, Tsukasa-san

298
00:18:50,275 --> 00:18:51,918
Do you like that girl?

299
00:18:51,918 --> 00:18:52,755
Huh?

300
00:18:52,755 --> 00:18:55,521
