whom you were chasing

301
00:18:55,521 --> 00:18:57,088
What are you saying all of a sudden?

302
00:18:57,088 --> 00:18:58,325
It won't happen.

303
00:19:01,481 --> 00:19:03,077
What?

304
00:19:03,077 --> 00:19:07,312
